Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Leiden is such a big city!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I got lost because there's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so many more roads than my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's easier to find a job\Nif you have a brooch from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to graduate and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you just want the brooch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, welcome to the\NAuto Memory Dolls' Training School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be considered absent\Non your second tardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the war is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the demand for Dolls\Nhas never been higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it is possible\Nto become a Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,without attending our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But our objective is not to train\Njust any Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It is to train you to become\Nthe best Doll you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Graduating from our school\Nis proof of excellence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if I do not deem you\Na worthy Doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you will never be given\Nthis certification.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite her doll-like outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,she had the demeanor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of a military soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An optimal Doll
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,must be able to type\Nas fast as someone speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter, Ms. Evergarden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You did not specify a speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can type if it's specified?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, type 200 characters\Nper minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not eating anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trained to keep my eating\Nto a minimum during a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some of mine then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Luculia from Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered me from my introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everyone's introductions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter-writing skills\Nan optimal Doll must have include
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge of grammar, vocabulary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and several forms and styles for letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I shall announce\Nyour evaluations for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Grammar results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect score. Violet Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, vocabulary results.\NAnother perfect score.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned from my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-How was school?\N-I bet you got in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. President, Instructor Rhodanthe\Nhas sent me home with today's results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You got excellent grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you get over it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one with the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them always fight like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really surprised you were able\Nto establish this company with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's class will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,actual training for writing\Non behalf of someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you ready?\N-Let us do our best, Ms. Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who do you want to address it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone I'd like to write a letter to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just choose someone close to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who you'd like to express\Nyour feelings to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone close?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please address it to Mr. Claudia Hodgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Claudia? Is that a friend? Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"That is all. This concludes my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"Have you received any new orders\Nfrom the major?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please add that at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds more like a report\Nthan a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it is your turn, Ms. Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's see. My bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'll address it to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to really thank\Nmy mother and father
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to express what you want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's time\Nto actually write the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and all the places\Nwe've been to together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the places we wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just so many to list.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"See you soon.\NYou don't need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sincerely, Luculia."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, read this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Father and Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it has been a while,\Nbut I have nothing specific to report."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"I worry that I have not expressed\Nmy gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for our previous engagements.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding the places we have been\Nand desire to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently working very diligently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently healthy and safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been no issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all. Please do not be concerned.\NLuculia."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And do you believe that is a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that I was too abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Letters are about communicating\Nsomeone's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,An optimal Doll will be able to decipher
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the person's true feelings\Nand express it on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your grades are excellent\Nand your typing is very fast and accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However, what you have written\Non her behalf cannot be called a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot call this a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-I could go aga...\N-That is all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, please hand these letters\Nto the people they are addressed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had an off day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been told the same thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you the best view in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always loved this view\Nsince I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.89,0:10:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be able to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that beautiful view in Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Luculia, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother! Were you drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-No!\N-Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a drink\Nbecause he won't let...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Spencer! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, I'm thankful for the letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but it feels more like a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My instructor also stated\Nthat it could not be called a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to become an optimal Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home. I can make dinner right a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Bluebell Junoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes.\N-Iberis Konoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia Marlborough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia Marlborough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations to the nine of you\Nfor graduating our program.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you all become optimal Dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Where are you going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work in my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.20,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Maybe I'll find something in Leiden.\N-What about you, Luculia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But you were the top of our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry to disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not graduating doesn't mean\Nyou can't become a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what was the purpose\Nfor going to the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,While it is true\Nthat graduating is not everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,if I'm unable to decipher...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the person's true feelings\Nand express it on paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no point in becoming a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here\Nwhen the program is over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I thought I could see you again\Nif I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Violet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the major?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You always ask at the end of your letters\Nif the major had sent a letter yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he the one you really\Nwant to send a letter to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we write a letter to him today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like your usual reports,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but a letter with your true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't leave until we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Major...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know\Nwhat I want to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I do not even understand\Nthe meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of the words he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, why did you want to become a Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... want to know what "I love you" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know what "I love you" means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to communicate\Nyour feelings, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, my parents died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The only family I have left...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When the war began,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother got drafted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't much fighting\Nin the Western Front
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,where he was deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The fighting was always taking place\Nfar away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the war didn't feel real to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,one day, when my parents\Nwent to Herne for business,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the Western Front was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't find any trace\Nof my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the war ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-My brother came home alive.\N-Come on, give me one drink at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be happy\Nthat at least he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-But...\N-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,my brother was angry that he wasn't able\Nto protect Herne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He blames himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for our parents' deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't show your face around here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,happy that he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to tell him "thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia, let's write a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put all your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,into a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever I think about telling him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing comes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll write your letter to the major\Nanother time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,An optimal Doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,will be able to decipher...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the person's true feelings\Nand express it on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Spencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Luculia's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's this?\N-It is a missio...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it is a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From Luculia to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,From Luculia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"To my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,LUCULIA MARLBOROUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you out so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a guild meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, aren't you done with school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I wrote a letter today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm not sure\Nif the feelings came across.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you two fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's this idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He put a wet cup on the letter\NI wrote for a client!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault\Nfor putting the letter there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with your attitude?\NI'm tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Instructor. I thought class was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm the one\Nwho asked her to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia showed me this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter you wrote\Non behalf of Luculia for her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The feelings I've been wanting\Nto tell my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, you were able to tell him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,An optimal Doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,will be able to decipher...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the person's true feelings\Nand express it on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to express a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you become an optimal Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter can sometimes be short and sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and still express important feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned from her\Nwhat the most important aspect...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of being a Doll is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a little odd\Nwith her doll-like outfits...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and acting like a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.12,0:22:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was a wonderful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NZensho Yamamoto
